name: The Touchdown Adventures of the Philae Lander
body:
### [Play the Game!](https://905aceeb74dfb7f058ee3eb1cc2def52e6873f46.googledrive.com/host/0B33ZyJNb2oUBTWJKeENOd1dqRmc/CMPM20_LanderProject-master/index.html target="blank")

### About
This game is a project for CMPM 20 at UCSC.  It has been created in HTML 5 and Javascript using the Phaser library.

### Authors and Contributors
Created by Nathan Irwin (@Mcfli), Dominic Balassone (@SydBal), George Rocha (@gjrocha), and Anderson Tu (@Enthrayu).
